title: Red Notice
summary: An Interpol-issued Red Notice is a global alert to hunt and capture the world's most wanted. But when a daring heist brings together the FBI's top profiler and two rival criminals, there's no telling what will happen.

title: We Can Be Heroes
summary: When alien invaders capture Earth's superheroes, their kids must learn to work together to save their parents - and the planet.

title: Army of the Dead
summary: Following a zombie outbreak in Las Vegas, a group of mercenaries take the ultimate gamble: venturing into the quarantine zone to pull off the greatest heist ever attempted.

title: Wish Dragon
summary: Din, a working-class college student, and Long, a cynical but all-powerful dragon capable of granting wishes, set off on a hilarious adventure through modern day Shanghai in pursuit of Din's long-lost childhood friend, Lina.

title: Army of Thieves
summary: A mysterious woman recruits bank teller Ludwig Dieter to lead a group of aspiring thieves on a top-secret heist during the early stages of the zombie apocalypse.

title: The Mitchells vs. The Machines
summary: After Katie Mitchell is accepted into the film school of her dreams, her family decides to use this opportunity to drive Katie to school as a road trip. When their plans are interrupted by a tech uprising, the Mitchells realize that they must work together to save the world.

title: Fatherhood
summary: A widowed new dad copes with doubts, fears, heartache and dirty diapers as he sets out to raise his daughter on his own.

title: The Unforgivable
summary: Released from prison into a society that won't forgive her past, a woman seeks redemption by searching for the sister she left behind.

title: The Guilty
summary: A troubled police detective demoted to 911 operator duty scrambles to save a distressed caller during a harrowing day of revelations â€” and reckonings.

title: Yes Day
summary: Parents attempt to make it through an entire day by only saying, yes to their children's requests.
